				<p class="postmetadata">26.10.2012 (Norbert Rost) Kategorie: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/allgemein/" title="Alle Beiträge in Allgemein ansehen" rel="category tag">Allgemein</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/presseschau/" title="Alle Beiträge in Presseschau ansehen" rel="category tag">Presseschau</a>  &middot; Tags: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/bgr/" rel="tag">BGR</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/fracking/" rel="tag">fracking</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/leonardo-maugeri/" rel="tag">Leonardo Maugeri</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/technology-review/" rel="tag">Technology Review</a>  &middot; <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/2012/10/technology-review-schiebt-oldiskussion-voran/#comments" title="Kommentiere Technology Review schiebt &#214;ldiskussion voran">8 Kommentare &#187;</a> </p>

